{"tid":687551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被鬧「港獨」「廢物」 Jackson發律師信要求網民道歉","createTime":"2018-06-02T11:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T11:07:30.000Z","uid":42804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3153ab916d3d7745f6686b1e044c6d55495b3d65","tid":687551,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180602&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58268453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180602%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58268453&d=mrgUYd5Ed7UwA6vG9LKaBf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a316a9e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180602%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58268453&h=d0a9f5c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180602&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58268453</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國男團GOT7嘅香港成員Jackson（王嘉爾）喺大陸人氣高企，佢亦要中韓兩邊走，近日有網民就喺微博發表大量具有侮辱性嘅言論，指摘Jackson愛講大話，留言包括「港獨」、「廢物」、「死爹」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\nJackson方面因為被網民侮辱，其工作室噚晚就喺官方微博發表律師信，針對部份微博用戶喺網上發佈有關Jackson不當嘅言論，直指網民嚴重侵犯咗Jackson嘅名譽權，同時要求有關網民要刪除相關言論並作出道歉，又呼籲：「網路不是謠言的避風港，願共同維護和諧自由的網路環境。」"},{"pid":"b66bf40d7be7da74e6cf1b78b97c5f901f1a164f","tid":687551,"uid":1863,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"小撚氣嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8992dd97b7def87d5f8157d408231685e2ba12fa","tid":687551,"uid":106336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"佢都港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明之前先影到用個印咗中國姨媽旗嘅頸枕係機場出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5ef9e095a804bd227980750da49a63d277b650","tid":687551,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"這就是中國 食得鹹魚"},{"pid":"9410969dc25feadbd25297dbc7e53fa454e5078c","tid":687551,"uid":72730,"lik